Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) cyugarije Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Umuryango w'Ubwongereza, kuva ku wa 1 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) cyibasiye ibihugu bitandukanye by'u Burayi/Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, ndetse n'ibindi bihugu by'isi byamaze igihe bigenzura icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Nyuma y'ibyabaye mu Butaliyani, ibitaro, amavuriro n'inzego z'ubuvuzi byagize ibyo bigerageza mu rwego rwo kongera umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi, ndetse n'ubundi bufasha bw'abaganga.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, habaye igitero cy'iterabwoba kitaramenyekana cyabereye mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'u Bushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari coronavirus nshya yari isanzwe izwi nka SARS-CoV-2 (Septuagint respiratory virus coronavirus 2).
Kuva icyo gihe, icyorezo cyatewe na SARS-CoV cyiswe icyorezo cya (COVI-19).
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko hafi 80% by'abantu bafite uburwayi budafite ubwandu, nk'ubw'ubuhumekero, kandi ko uburwayi bwose bufite ubwandu.
Mu 14% by'abandura, COVID-19 yatumye barwara indwara zikomeye cyane ku buryo batagombaga kuguma mu bitaro, naho mu 6% by'abandura, byatewe n'ibibazo by'ubuzima, bityo bakaba bagomba kwitabwaho n'abaganga.
Imfu z'abarwayi bari mu bitaro ba COVID-19 zigera kuri 4%.
Muri iki cyigisho, twasuzumye aho icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyageze mu bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Umuryango w'Abibumbye (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza (UK) dukurikije uko cyagenze mu mujyi wa Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ndimo ndasuzuma imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'abo mu Butaliyani kuva ku wa 31 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK
Nyuma y'Ubushinwa, COVID-19 yafashe indi ntera, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ubu kirimo gukurikira.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Mu itangazo ry'urubuga rwa Eurosurveillance ryo ku wa 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri al. yatangaje ko ari bwo bwa mbere mu Burayi hemejwe icyorezo cya COVID-19 nk'uko bitangazwa na OMS.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA, icyorezo cya mbere cy'uburwayi bwa gatatu cyibasiye u Bufaransa cyatangajwe ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu baturage bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari bamaze kumenyekana mu bihugu 30 bigize EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 habayeho abantu 39 768 banduye ndetse n'abantu 1 727 bapfuye, mu gihe mu Butaliyani habayeho abantu 1 441.
Gushyiraho imibare y'abanduye COVID-19
Ishami ry'u Burayi ryita ku kurwanya indwara (ECDC), rivuga ko imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, ishingiye ku makuru yatanzwe n'inzego zishinzwe ubuzima, inzego z'ibanze n'iz'ibanze hamwe na OMS, izaba isuzumwa saa munani z'amanywa.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu kugereranya ubuzima n'ubw'u Butaliyani.
Nk'uko tugiye gusuzuma imibare y'abanduye COVID-19, twashyize hamwe imibare y'abanduye COVID-19, hanyuma twasanze icyiciro cya COVID-19 mu bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Twagaragaje kandi umubare w'abanduye mu bihugu bitandukanye ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani z'amanywa, aho harimo n'u Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza.
Iterambere mu mibare y'ibanze y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA mu minsi 14 n'u Bwongereza byakurikiwe cyane n'ibyavuye mu Ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, ugera ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibindi bikoresho).
Ibi bitangazwa ahanini n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani, mu gihe ibindi bihugu byose byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza byatangaje ko hari indi mibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 (Izindi nkomoko).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19, mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, aho byashyizwe mu byiciro bibiri, n'Ubutaliyani kuva ku wa 31 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani z'amanywa, ibihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'ibindi bihugu byo mu Bwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye mu minsi itatu mbere cyangwa nyuma y'uko u Butaliyani bufata iki cyemezo.
Ibi biragaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 bataravugwa mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA n'Ubwongereza.
Ibipimo by'ubukana n'ubwiyongere bwa COVID-19 bigaragaza ko icyorezo gihuza n'ibipimo bishobora gukemurwa mu bihugu byose.
Ibi biterwa n'uko ibihugu byagiye bihinduka, impinduka mu byemezo by'ubuvuzi bw'igihugu, ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu mu bihugu bitandukanye n'uburyo bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gusuzumwa COVID-19, no gusuzumwa.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'icyorezo basanze 10% by'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'ibanze, kandi amakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'inzego z'ubuvuzi mu bice byibasiwe n'icyorezo bikomeje kubikora.
Amakuru y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bitaro no mu bigo byita ku barwayi, ari mu byiciro bya EU/EEA bya 6% na 1%, byombi (ni ukuvuga ko amakuru ari mu byiciro by'ingenzi).
Nanone kandi, ibyo byose bishyirwa hamwe mu rwego rumwe kugira ngo hakorwe inyandiko z'ibanze zigaragaza umubare w'abanduye n'uw'abamaze gupfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-2011 bwerekanye itandukaniro ry'umubare w'ibitanda n'amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi ku barwayi bakomeye n'abari mu cyiciro cy'ubudehe mu Burayi, kuva ku bitanda 29.2 mu Budage kugeza kuri 4.2 ku bantu 100 000 muri Portugal.
Ibi bihugu bishobora kuba bikennye cyangwa se bifite ubukungu buciriritse kurusha u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda by'ubuvuzi ku bantu 100 000 mu 2010-11).
Gushyiraho gahunda zigenga uburyo bwo kwakira abarwayi, harimo ko buri gihugu cya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza bishobora kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kujya kwa muganga ndetse n'abashaka ibitanda bagomba kuba bafite amabwiriza yo kwita ku muntu nibura 90% by'ibiro bya ECDC by'igenzura ry'indwara ya COVID-19.
Kubera ko umubare w'abandura wiyongereye mu bice bimwe by'ibihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/EEA ndetse no mu bindi bice by'Ubwongereza, ndetse n'ibitaro n'amashyirahamwe y'abarwayi akorera mu byumba by'ababyeyi, amakuru y'abarwayi n'ibitanda by'abarwayi biboneka ku wa kabiri w'icyumweru mu mijyi yose mu rwego rw'umutekano wa 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibiri kuba mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyakomeje kwiyongera mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA ndetse no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibigo nderabuzima n'inzego zishinzwe kwita ku barwayi bigomba kwitegura uburyo bwo gufasha abaturage kubera SARS-CoV-2 n'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi, ndetse n'ubundi bufasha, nk'uko bigaragara mu bice by'u Butaliyani by'icyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe kurwanya icyorezo cya ECDC, hari uburyo budafite aho bugarukira mu gukumira ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2, ndetse n'uburyo bwo kuva mu buvuzi kugera mu kugabanya, kuko umubare w'abandura wiyongera ku buryo utanga umwanya uhagije ku bakora ibizamini byo kuvura kugira ngo basobanukirwe, bitabire kandi bahindure uburyo bwabo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo mu gihe cyagenwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'ubuzima bw'igihugu kandi bwerekana uburyo leta ifite bwo kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo.
