Ubuyapani bwatanze impapuro zo kwipfuka mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Turukiya yatanze imfashanyo y'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwatanze toni zisaga 13 z'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze miliyoni 18 z'ibikoresho byo kwipfuka mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwatanze toni 17.8 z'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zitanga toni 17.8 z'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, ndetse zitanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'Amerika mu rwego rw'imfashanyo n'amafaranga mu bihugu byibasiwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abaganga kugira ngo bafashe u Butaliyani mu ntambara yo kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Perezida Jack Ma yatanze ibyangombwa bya miliyoni 1.1 by'ibipimo, miliyoni 6 z'ibisuko, n'ibyangombwa by'ibyangombwa 60,000 by'ibyangombwa i Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia, byateganyijwe gukwirakwizwa n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho bya 5 000, amakariso 100 000 n'ibyangombwa 5 byo guhumeka mu kirere muri Panama.
Nanone kandi, yafashije Kanada mu bijyanye n'imiti. U Buholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque byashyize ahagaragara ibibazo by'imiti yo mu maso ikoreshwa mu Bushinwa n'ibikoresho by'igerageza.
Urugero, Espagne yatanze ibikoresho 58 000 by'ibanze byakozwe mu Bushinwa byerekanaga ko byuzuye ku kigero cya 30%, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwatanze ibikoresho 600 000 by'ibanga by'Abashinwa byerekanaga ko byuzuye.
U Bubiligi bwakoze ibishushanyo by'ibishushanyo by'amaso bitabasha kwambara 100.000 nyuma yo kuboneka mu gihugu cya Colombia.
Mu gihe kimwe, ubufasha bw'Ubushinwa bwashyizwe mu bikorwa mu bice bimwe by'Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Umuryango w'Abibumbye washinze ibikorwa by'ubutabazi by'ubutabazi mu bihugu byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo.
OMS yashimye cyane ingamba leta y'Ubushinwa yafashe zo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
OMS yasobanuye itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho bavugaga ko leta y'Ubushinwa yakoze ibishoboka byose kugira ngo ikomeze gushyiraho ingamba zo kugenzura no gukumira icyorezo, n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya SARS aho leta y'u Bushinwa "yatangaga amakuru ku bantu batatu mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku gitekerezo cya guverinoma yo hagati cyo guhagarika ibikorwa byo gupima i Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko "ibyiyumvo by'abakoraga ubushakashatsi", ari "igitekerezo cy'ingenzi cyo guhagarika icyorezo ku rwego rw'icyorezo gikomeye kurusha ibindi" maze agita "ikitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima".Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko umuntu yanduye umuntu hanze y'u Bushinwa no kwiyongera kw'imibare y'abandura mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo cya mbere ku Isi (PHEIC), ku nshuro ya mbere kuva PHEIC yafatwa nk'icyorezo mu 2009.
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa WHO, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC ishobora "kwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite ubukungu buciriritse n'ibikennye, bidakeneye serivisi z'ubuzima.
Mu gusubiza ku kugabanuka kw'ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu zo guhagarika ingendo n'ubucuruzi hagati y'ibihugu" kandi ko "WHO isaba ko hagabanywa ubucuruzi cyangwa ubwikorezi".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga ko wafasha ibihugu bikennye by'ibihumbi 675 by'amadolari, mu rwego rwo kwihutisha ibikorwa byo gufasha ibihugu "bifite uburyo budafite uburyo bwo kuvura, aho byabereye hose".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "dukomeye nk'ingingo zacu zidafite imbaraga" asaba isi yose "kwihangana ubu cyangwa se kwihangana mu gihe kiri imbere".Ku wa 11 Gashyantare, OMS mu nama y'itangazamakuru yashyizeho COVID-19 nk'icyorezo.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa ONU António Guterres yemeye gutanga "umusanzu wose wa politiki wa ONU mu gisubizo".
Hari indi miryango ya ONU ishinzwe kurwanya indwara ikora nk'igisubizo, ikora nk'umuryango w'abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko izaba ifite inshingano zo "gukemura ibibazo by'ubuzima mu gihe ibindi bihugu bishobora gukoresha ubumenyi bwabyo mu gukemura ibibazo by'icyorezo mu baturage bose, ndetse n'umutungo wacu wose".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, hashyizweho itsinda ry'abakozi bahuza Ubushinwa mu rwego rwo guha impuguke z'amahanga na OMS mu Bushinwa gufasha mu kwirinda no gupima "icyorezo no gukwirakwiza" mu gihugu hagati no guhuza ibigo by'ubushakashatsi by'ikirenga n'ibindi bihugu byo hanze kugira ngo "byibanze ku bikorwa by'intara n'imijyi, imijyi n'uturere".Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yavuze ko "isi igomba gushyiraho gahunda yo gutegura icyorezo cya coronavirus", ivuga ko mu gihe isi yari mu nzira yo guhangana n'icyorezo, igihugu cyari mu "cyiciro cya mbere cyo gutegura".
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza icyorezo cya Iran, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'abakozi ba ONU kugira ngo rigenzure uko iki cyorezo cyagenze.Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS batangaje ko ibipimo by'icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi bizatangira kuva ku "gushyira hasi" kugeza ku "gushyira hasi", ari na byo bizaba intangiriro y'ibizamini by'icyorezo.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi ushinzwe gahunda z'ubutabazi bw'ibanze za WHO, yavuze mu nkuru imwe ko "Bimeze nk'isuzuma rimwe ku butegetsi bwose bw'isi: Tugomba kwemera.
Iyi virusi ishobora kwibasira isi kandi igomba guhagarara, " binyuze mu gushyiraho ingamba zo guhagarika izongera gutuma isi "isubira inyuma".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu azatuma abayobozi b'ubuzima barushaho guhangana n'icyorezo, avuga ko aya makuru asobanura ko "twemeranyije ko buri muntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura iyi virusi".
Muri Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye yavuze ko OMS "yagize uruhare rukomeye mu guhangana n'icyorezo, ndetse no mu guhangana n'ikibazo cy'umutekano". OMS ishobora gutanga ibisobanuro by'ingenzi ku bijyanye n'ibikenewe mu gucunga icyorezo, ndetse n'ibikenewe mu kwihutisha ubuzima rusange no gushyira virusi mu byiciro by'icyorezo.
Ibi birego kandi byibanda ku ibaruwa yo gusaba umuyobozi mukuru wa WHO, Tedros Adhanom, ko yandika ibaruwa y'ikiruhuko cy'izabukuru, yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, impuguke mu by'imiterere y'abantu muri ONU zateguye inama y'ibanze yo gusesengura imiterere y'abantu muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Abadepite bemeza ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gufata umwanzuro wo gufunga undi, kandi ko leta ifite uburenganzira bwo kubikora.
Iri shyirahamwe ryemeza ko uburyo bwo kwirinda cyangwa kwirinda kuvurwa bidakwiriye kuba uburyo bwo guca urwa kibera.
Abahanga bavuga ko abantu bose bafite ibibazo by'ubuzima, harimo abafite ubumuga bwo mu nda, abantu bo mu matsinda mato, abageze mu za bukuru, abantu bahinduye imibereho yabo mu gihugu, abantu badafite aho baba, abantu bakorera mu bigo by'ubutabazi, abafunzwe, abashinzwe umutekano n'abandi bantu bashinzwe ubufasha bwa leta.
Ibigo bya leta ku isi birimo birwanaho mu guhangana n'ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza byatewe n'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye gishinzwe iterambere ry'igihugu cyashyizeho uburyo bwo gutanga amakuru arambuye kandi ku gihe ku bijyanye n'imikorere ya politiki ku isi hose, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'ibitekerezo.
Uhereye ku ngamba zo gukemura ibibazo by'ubuzima n'umutekano ku isi kugeza ku guhangana n'ikibazo cyo kuguma mu rugo no kugabanya ingendo, ibikorwa by'ishami ry'ubufatanye, harimo na Politiki y'Igihugu, bigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga uko byitwara no guhuza ibisubizo by'isi yose kuri coronavirus.
