Abayobozi b'intara zimwe na zimwe b'ishyaka rya gikomunisti ry'Ubushinwa (CPC) bazakora iperereza kugira ngo bashobore kugenzura uko abantu bakwirakwira mu Burasirazuba bw'Ubushinwa, imiterere y'icyorezo n'uburyo bwo gusubiza politiki y'icyorezo mu turere.
