Ikinyamakuru cy'Abataliyani La Stampa cyatangaje ko "hari politiki ikomeye" ariko nticyatangaza ko 80% by'ubufasha bw'Uburusiya ari "ibidakwiye cyangwa bidafite akamaro kanini mu Butaliyani".
