Ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19 ku kazi
Ibipimo by'ibyago byo mu kazi biterwa na COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo gukorana mu by'ubuzima no kwirinda icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Ibimenyetso by'ibyago mu kazi biratandukana bitewe n'aho ukorera n'uburyo ukoreramo, bitewe n'igenzura ry'ibyago byo kuba, ubwandu mu baturage, n'ibintu bishobora gutuma abakozi bashobora kwandura COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe umutekano n'ubuzima (OSHA) kivuga ko ibikorwa byoroheje bitagira ibyago byo guhura n'abantu benshi cyangwa abakozi, aho ingamba zo kwirinda icyorezo zisabwa, nko gukaraba intoki, gutuma abakozi bake mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guhumeka neza, no gukora isuku ku kazi.
Ibikorwa bishobora guteza ubwandu byibanda ku bantu bahura cyangwa bagirana isano ya hafi na COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe no kwanduza abantu muri rusange cyangwa se bavuye mu ngendo mu mahanga.
Ibi birimo abakozi bafite ubushobozi bwo guhuza n'abaturage nko mu mashuri, ahantu hakorera abantu benshi, ahantu hakorerwa ibikorwa byinshi by'ubucuruzi.
Ibyago by'iki cyiciro, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda, harimo guhumeka binyuze mu mabwiriza yo kwirinda imyanda yandura, imyenda ipfuka umusatsi, no kwambara imyenda y'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe uhuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima n'abakora mu by'ubuvuzi bapfuye nk'abafite cyangwa umuntu ushobora kuba afite COVID-19 ari bo bafite ibyago byo kwandura, bikongera ibyago byo gupfa iyo abakozi bakora imibonano mpuzabitsina ituma umuntu atakaza aerosol, cyangwa se akanywa, cyangwa agakora ku miti, umuntu ufite cyangwa ushobora kuba afite COVID-19.
Ibyangombwa by'ibyago by'abakozi nk'aba birimo kubungabunga ibyangombwa by'ubwubatsi nk'ibyumba by'ubushyuhe, hamwe n'ibyangombwa by'ubushyuhe bijyanye n'akazi.
COVID-19 ishobora guteza akaga gakomeye ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kuba batagikora kubera ko banduye, kubera ko baba bashaka kwita ku bandi, cyangwa kubera ko batinya ko bashobora kwandura.
Ibicuruzwa bishobora guhinduka bitewe n'ibikoresho bicuruzwa, uburyo bwo kubikura (urugero: kubikura mu gihe ibicuruzwa bihenze, cyangwa kubikura mu rugo cyangwa mu modoka.
Mu gusoza, gutumiza ibikoresho mu turere twibasirwa cyane na COVID-19 bishobora guhagarikwa. Gutegura cyangwa gusubiza icyorezo bishobora gufasha mu kubungabunga ibikorwa.
Iyo gahunda igamije kugabanya ibyago by'uburwayi bijyana n'aho umuntu akorera ndetse n'ibindi bikorwa nk'ibyo, urugero nk'ubwandu, ibintu bishobora kongera ibyago byo mu rugo mu muryango, n'ibintu bishobora kongera ibyago by'abantu biyahura nk'uburwayi cyangwa indwara zikurikira.
Nanone kandi, bashyizeho ingamba zo kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura, kandi bashyizeho gahunda yo kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'ibintu bishobora kuba byarabaye.
Gutegura no gushyiraho gahunda zo guhangana n'icyorezo bishobora gutandukana bitewe n'igihugu cyangwa intara.
Uburyo bwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo harimo kwirinda kwanduza abakozi, abita ku bandi bantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura indwara runaka, gukomeza ubucuruzi, no kugabanya ibyago ku bandi bantu mu gihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina.
Indwara mu baturage ba ruganda igira ingaruka ku buryo bwo gutunganya ibintu.
Imikorere yo kugenzura ibyago ni uburyo bukoreshwa mu nzego z'ubuzima no kwita ku buzima kugira ngo imikorere y'ubugenzuzi ikorwe n'itsinda kandi igire akamaro.
Mu gihe COVID-19 idashobora gukurwaho, ingamba z'ingenzi ni ukwitegura mu buryo bw'ubwubatsi, hakurikiyeho kugenzura ibikorwa, hanyuma hakagira ibikorwa byo gufunga.
Imikorere y'ubwubatsi igamije kurinda abakozi guhangana n'akaga gashingiye ku kazi, ariko ntibitekereze ku myitwarire y'abakoresha, kandi bishobora kuba ari uburyo bwiza bwo kubikora.
Imikorere y'akazi ni ihinduka mu miyoborere y'akazi cyangwa mu mabwiriza areba uburenganzira bw'umukozi cyangwa umukozi.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri (PPE) ni nk'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi, ariko bishobora no gukoreshwa mu bindi bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi.
Buri PPE igomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku ngaruka ku muntu, hagendewe ku bintu by'ingenzi (urugero nk'ibyangombwa by'isuku), bikoreshwa mu buryo bworoshye kandi bworoshye, bigenzurwa, bikonorwa, kandi bigasimbuzwa igihe gikwiye, bikurwaho mu buryo bworoshye, bikonorwa, cyangwa bigasimbuzwa abandi bantu.
Dukurikije ibivugwa n'Ikigo cy'Amerika Gishinzwe Umutekano n'Ubuzima mu Mwuga (OSHA), akazi katagira ibimenyetso byinshi gafite ingaruka mbi ku baturage cyangwa ku bandi bakozi.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda icyorezo mu kazi ni nko gukaraba intoki neza kandi ku gihe, kubwira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, kwirinda guhumeka mu gihe cyo kwipfuka no gukaraba, gutanga amakariso n'umushinga wo gukaraba, gutegura guhinduranya imibereho cyangwa guhunga mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, kwirinda ko abakozi bakoresha ibikoresho cyangwa ibikoresho by'abandi, no gusukura no gukora isuku aho bakorera.
Kumenya no kwirinda abantu banduye ni intambwe y'ingenzi mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abimukira n'abandi mu kazi.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'uburwayi (CDC) cyasabye ko abakozi bafite ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero bidashobora kugaragara baguma mu rugo kugeza igihe umubiri wabo uzongera kugaragara, ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero, cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso nyuma y'amasaha 24 batarafata imiti igabanya ubuhumekero cyangwa ibindi bimenyetso, kandi ko bagomba kubanza kwibuka ko indwara idashobora kugaragara, bagatanga ikiruhuko ku bakozi baguma mu rugo kugira ngo bita ku babyeyi babo barwaye, kandi ko bahabwa uburenganzira bwo kubikora.
Ku rwego rwa OSHA, ibikorwa by'ingutu birimo abantu bashaka kwegera abantu bari mu ntera ya metero esheshatu (1.8 m) bafite cyangwa bashobora kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kuba baranduye SARS-CoV-2 kubera ko yandurira mu baturage mu gihe cy'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi, cyangwa kubera ko umuntu uherutse gukora urugendo mu mahanga yandura COVID-19.
Ibi birimo abakozi ba hafi y'abaturage nk'amashuri, ahantu hakora abantu benshi, n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi aho ibikoresho by'ubucuruzi byuzuyemo imyanda. Gusuzuma kwa injeniyeri ku byerekeye imyanda n'amatsinda y'abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura birimo kugabanya ibikoresho byo guhumeka, kongera umwuka, kugabanya imyanda nka plasitiki yo guhumeka, no kugabanya inzugi ku modoka z'ubucuruzi. Gusuzuma ku kazi ku buryo bwihutirwa n'amatsinda y'abantu bafite ibyago byo kwandura birimo guhumeka abakozi banduye mu rugo, guhindura imyitwarire y'abakozi mu nzu cyangwa mu nzu cyangwa mu cyumba, kwirinda abakiriya mu cyumba, no gutanga serivisi z'ubutabazi mu gihe kirekire, nko kugabanya ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19, gutanga amakuru, gutanga ibyangombwa by'ibanze, gutanga amafoto, gukora imibonano, no gutanga serivisi zo kwirinda COVID-19, no kubumbatira ibikorwa by'ubutabazi.
Abakozi bo muri iri tsinda bakeneye amabwiriza yo gutangira.
Iyo umuntu yanduye mu ndege, ingamba z'ingenzi zo kurinda abakozi n'abandi bantu bafasha abagenzi harimo gushyira umurwayi mu kato, kumureka agashyirwamo ibirenge 6, kumushyiraho undi muntu wo kumwitaho, no kumuha agapfukamunwa cyangwa kumwigisha ko agomba gupfuka umunwa n'amaso n'igishura mu gihe asoma cyangwa anuka.
Abakozi ba Kabin bagomba kwambara udukingirizo tw'amaboko nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi w'umunyamibembe cyangwa se ku mubiri cyangwa ku mubiri wanduye, mu gihe bishoboka, ndetse n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi mu gihe umurwayi afite uburwayi, guhumeka bidashira cyangwa ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Ibipfamatwi bigomba gushyirwa mu byumba bikorerwamo ibyo bikoresho, kandi ibirenge byanduye bigomba guhanagurwa no gukorerwa isuku.Mu gihe cyo kwirinda kwinjiza ibicuruzwa mu masoko, nko mu ndege cyangwa ahandi hatagira abantu, kwirinda icyorezo birimo kwirinda gutwara umuntu mu gihe yanduye, kwirinda guhagarara kure no kumenyesha abashinzwe ubuzima igihe urwaye.
Mu rugero runaka, ubu buryo bwo kwirinda bushobora gukoreshwa mu cyumba cyihariye. Ku bijyanye n'amashuri n'amashuri yigisha abana, CDC isaba ko hashyirwaho igihe gito cyo gufunga kugira ngo umuntu ugiye kwivuza cyangwa kwivuza mu gihe umuntu wanduye ari mu cyumba cy'ishuri nta kibazo cyo gukwirakwiza mu baturage.
Iyo hari ubwandu buke mu baturage, gahunda yo kubarinda ishobora kuba ingirakamaro nko guhagarika ingendo, gutunganya, no guhuza abantu n'abandi nko gukora siporo, kurira cyangwa kunywa ku byokurya, kongera amashyiga hagati y'ibitaro, kugabanya igihe cyo kugera no gutandukana, kubuza abantu kujya cyangwa kuva mu bitaro, no guhagarika kuvurira mu bitaro abana bafite ibimenyetso bya virusi itera SIDA.
Iyo hagize ubwandu bwa mbere mu baturage bo mu karere, nyuma y'ingamba zo kwirinda, igihe cyo gufunga amashuri gishobora kongerwa. Ku birebana n'abantu bose bakwirakwiza icyorezo, CDC ivuga ko ibyago by'ubuzima by'ibanze byafashwe.
Abantu bakorana n'abantu bafite cyangwa bashobora kuba bafite COVID-19 basabwa gukurikiza amabwiriza y'abakozi b'ubuzima, harimo kwambara ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi.
