ACE2 ihagarika imikorere ya angiotensin converting hormone (ACE) binyuze mu kugabanya umuvuduko wa angiotensin-II no kongera Ang ((1-7)), bigatuma iba umuti ushobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikora nk'umwimerere mu maraso y'izindi virusi.
Umubiri w'umuntu ukunze kuvugwaho cyane nka hACE2.
Ingirabuzimafatizo 2 ihindura Angiotensin ni metalloenzime ifite zinc kandi iba ku gice cy'umubiri cya endothelium n'izindi ngirabuzimafatizo.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ifite umurongo wa N-terminal peptidase M2 hamwe n'umurongo wa C-terminal collectrin wa amino acid transporter.
ACE2 ni poroteyine yo mu bwoko bwa I, ifite uruhu rukora kandi iherereye mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'ingingo mu bihaha no mu bindi bikoresho.
Urubuga rwa ACE2 rwo hanze y'ingirabuzimafatizo ruhuza urubuga rwa transmembrane n'ikindi kimenyetso cyitwa sheddase, kandi poroteyine z'ibanze zikomeza kuba mu maraso kandi amaherezo zikurwaho n'uruhu.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifitanye isano n'uruhu rw'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo nyinshi z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ubwoko bwa II, intake ntoya za enterocyte, insoro z'amaraso n'iz'amaraso n'iz'amaraso mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
