Umurimo w'ibanze wa ACE2 ni uguhindura ACE.
ACE ikora mu buryo bwo kuvura angiotensin I ikora mu buryo bwo kuvura angiotensin II.
ACE2 nayo ihindura amino acid ya carboxyl-terminal phenylalanine mu buryo bw'ibanze ikoreshwa na angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) ikoreshwa na angiotensin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora no guhindura indi peptides nka [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A, na ghrelin.
ACE2 nayo ihindura imiterere ya SLC6A19 ya amino acid idakora kandi ishobora kuba ari yo iteza indwara ya Hartnup.
Nk'umushinga wa transmembrane, ACE2 ikora nk'umunyururu umwe mu byiciro by'imiterere y'izindi virusi, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi itera SARS); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi itera COVID-19).
Nanone kandi, gusangira poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 mu gice cya enzymatic cya ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'ingirabuzimafatizo, byatumye habaho intangabuzima (endocytosis) no guhindura imiterere y'izo virusi byombi mu bice by'ingenzi by'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Ubu bushakashatsi bwemeje ko protein S ikorwa na TMPRSS2 serine protease receptor, ubu bushakashatsi bukaba bugamije kuvura iyi ndwara.
Icyakora, imiryango myinshi y'abahanga n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura ibiyobyabwenge zasabye ko hakomeza gukoreshwa imiti isanzwe yo mu rwego rwa ACE inhibitor na ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko "kuvurwa hakoreshejwe imiti ya ACE inhibitors byagabanyije ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ibicurane ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'ubundi buryo".
Ikindi kandi, "ibyago byo kwandura pneumonia byagabanutse ku barwayi bavurwa n'abazimya ACE bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura pneumonia, cyane cyane ku barwayi bafite ikibazo cy'amaraso n'imitsi yo mu bwonko ndetse n'indwara z'umutima.
Gufata inibya ACE nabyo byagiye bifatanya mu kugabanya urupfu rw'abandura pneumonia, nubwo ibimenyetso byerekana ko nta ngaruka ya pneumonia yose".
Recombinant human ACE2 (rhACE2) ni umuti mushya wo kurwanya indwara z'ubuhumekero, kandi ushobora gutuma amaraso y'umuntu agira ubushyuhe bwinshi mu gihe cyo guhumeka no guhumeka mu bana bafite ubumuga bwo kutabona neza, bafite ubumuga bwo mu nda buterwa na lipopolysaccharide.
Imibereho y'igice cya kabiri cya rhACE2 mu bantu ni hafi amasaha 10 n'iminota 30 yo gutangira gukora, ndetse n'igihe cyo kwiyongera (igihe) mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwakozwe bwerekana ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti w'ingenzi mu bantu batagaragaza ubushobozi bwo kwakira imiti ya classique yo mu rwego rwa angiotensin-deficiency system (RAS inhibitors) cyangwa mu barwayi barwaye angiotensin II.
b'Ibikoresho bya COVID-19 ni porogaramu zashyizweho mu rwego rwo gufasha abantu kumenya amakuru y'abantu mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, nk'uko byasobanuwe mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubugenzuzi bw'abantu ("abagenzi") bashobora kuba bari kumwe n'umuntu wanduye.
Hariho ibindi bikorwa byakozwe cyangwa byatangijwe, bifashishije leta n'abikorera mu nzego z'ibanze n'iz'ibanze.
Hakozwe ubushakashatsi ku buryo bwo gusobanura uburyo bwo gukwirakwiza ibitabo.
Ibibazo by'ubwizerwe byatangiye, cyane cyane ku buryo bwo kumenya aho abantu bakoresha iyo porogaramu baba.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya amakuru yerekeranye n'umuntu ukoresha Bluetooth kugirango utandukane n'izindi telefoni.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje icyarimwe ko bizashyiraho ibikoresho byunganira porogaramu zifite Bluetooth muri sisitemu z'imikorere za Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa, ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu ituma abaturage bamenya niba bahuye n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Abantu bakoresha iyi porogaramu mu migi 200 yo mu Bushinwa.
Iyi porogaramu yashyizweho n'umuryango wa IT, igaragara ko ifunguye ku bantu bose kandi igatangwa na leta.Muri Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru hari porogaramu ikorana na Bluetoth yitwa "StopKorona!", igamije kwerekana ibyago by'ubushyamirane bw'abantu banduye no gutanga igisubizo cyuzuye ku buyobozi bw'ubuzima.
Iri rushanwa ryakozwe n'abakozi bo mu nzego z'ubucuruzi n'ikoranabuhanga n'ubuzima.
Ku ya 14 Mata 2020, iyi porogaramu yari itegereje kwakira Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo kwirinda icyorezo izajya ikoreshwa mu byumweru bike.
Australia na New Zealand barimo gusuzuma ibipimo bishingiye ku bumenyi bwa TraceTogether Singapore hamwe na BlueTrace.Uburusiya buteganya gushyiraho uburyo bwo gupima abarwayi ba COVID-19 bari i Moscow, kugira ngo bamenye niba bashobora kuva mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu muri kaminuza ya Cambridge wigisha iby'ubwubatsi n'umutekano, yavuze ko ibibazo by'imikorere bishobora guterwa n'imikoreshereze y'ibikoresho, urugero nko kumenya niba umuntu yaranduye ariko atari byo, ari ingenzi cyane iyo bigizwe n'abantu bake.
Mu gihe Apple yari ifite impungenge z'uko hashobora kugaragara porogaramu za "coronavirus" zidakora neza cyangwa zangiza, yashyizeho imipaka ku buryo ibigo bishobora kongera porogaramu za "coronavirus" ku isoko rya App, bikazirinda "kugenzura" cyangwa ku zindi nzego.
Google na Amazon bakoze ubushakashatsi nk'ubwo.
Abashakashatsi ku kibazo cy'ubwizerwe bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye no kwirinda abantu bose bakoresheje ikoranabuhanga rya coronavirus, cyane cyane niba uburyo bwo kwirinda bwagaragajwe mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo cya coronavirus buzahagarara mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe asaga 100 yavuguruje ibyo birego by'ubutabera.
Aya mashyirahamwe yatangaje impungenge ku bikorwa bya leta:
kugenzura bishobora kuba "gukenewe, bifite akamaro kandi byemewe";
gushyiraho gahunda yo kugenzura no kugenzura ibivugwa mu mabwiriza yo kugenzura;
ibikorwa n'amakuru by'ubufatanye mu bijyanye na COVID-19.
umutekano w'amakuru kandi nta kwiyitirira izina bizakorwa mu buryo bwo kubika amakuru kandi bizakorwa mu buryo buhuje n'ibyavuye mu bikorwa;
kugenzura amakuru mu buryo buhoraho no mu buryo bworoshye
gusangiza abandi amakuru yose, bigomba gufatirwa ku buryo bushyize mu gaciro
uburyo bwo guhagarika guhagarika no guhagarika ibikorwa by'abaturage byo kwishyura;
Gushyira hamwe kw'abantu bose muri gahunda binyuze mu "bakozi bakomeye" bigomba guhuzwa, nk'uko bikorwa n'abakozi b'ubuzima hamwe n'amatsinda yemewe. Ikigo cy'ubucuruzi cy'ikoranabuhanga cy'Abadage (CCC) na Reporters Without Borders (Reporter ohne Grenzen) (RSF) na bo batanze ibitekerezo.
Gahunda ya Google/Apple igamije gukemura ikibazo cy'umutekano muke mu gukuraho uburyo bwo kumenya aho umuntu ari mu gihe cyo gutumiza amabaruwa nyuma y'igihe runaka.
Ibihugu bimwe bikoresha amategeko yo kugenzura ariko ntibikoreshe porogaramu, ibyo bikaba byarabaye ntawe uhinduye porogaramu mu buryo butari bukurikizwe nyuma.
Muri Isirayeli, gahunda yo kwirinda no gushyiraho amategeko yemewe.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura aho umuntu ari bushobora gutuma abantu batakaza amakuru.
Icyakora, ntabwo gahunda zose n'amabwiriza y'ibanze bisaba ko umuntu agira amakuru y'aho ari; hari uburyo bwo kubika amakuru butangwa n'amabwiriza y'ibanze yo guhanahana amakuru (mu matsinda ari hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, hari uburyo bwo gukemura ikibazo cy'ubushomeri.
Hakurikijwe ikoreshwa rya porogaramu, urwego rushobora gukusanya amakuru y'ubushakashatsi binyuze mu buryo butandukanye, urugero nk'amakuru y'aho telefoni iri n'amakuru y'ikarita y'igiciro, kandi bikayashyira hamwe kugirango byemeze ubutumwa bw'ubutumwa ku bantu bashobora kuba barwaye.
Uretse gukoresha amakuru y'ibanze, leta yashyizeho amakuru y'ibanze agenewe abantu bose, mu gihe hari impinduka n'amabwiriza ku makuru nyuma y'icyorezo cya MERS mu gihugu.
Aya makuru afunguwe ku mugaragaro binyuze mu bikorwa byinshi n'amabwiriza. Ibihugu nka Ubudage byateguye guhuza uburyo bwo kubika amakuru n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga.
Tariki 6 Mata 2020, amakuru azasohoka uko yakabaye.
Gusuzuma aho amakuru yafatiwe n'ibanga biramenyekana, kandi abashakashatsi basanze byibuze abantu 13 aribo bakoresha uburyo bwo kubika amakuru, harimo gukoresha Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) mu gusuzuma abakoresha telefoni.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni imbaraga zashyizweho zigizwe n'uburyo bw'ibanze n'ubw'ibanze, kandi ntabwo ari uburyo bumwe.Ibikorwa byogeye harimo Decentralized Privacy-Preserving Proximity Tracing (DP-PPT/DP-3T), Temporary Contact Numbers (TCN, ahazwi nka Contact Event Numbers, CEN), Privacy Sensitive Protocols and Mechanisms for Mobile Contact Tracing (PACT), n'ibindi.
Muri ubwo buryo, amakuru ashobora kuboneka ntaba ari mu cyiciro, kandi imikorere yose iba ishingiye kuri icyo cyiciro.
Itsinda ry'ibanga muri MIT Media Lab ririmo gukemura ikibazo cy'ibanga rya SafePaths, uburyo bwo gukoresha uburyo bwo kubika amakuru mu gihe cyo gutoranya amakuru no gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari n'uburyo bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Hari ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku gitabo cy'ubuntu cyitwa "Apps Gone Rogue: Maintaining Personal Privacy in an Epidemic" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020.
SafeTrace ikora ikoranabuhanga rituma abakozi bashobora guhana amakuru yerekeye aho batuye n'ubuzima bwabo n'abandi bantu ndetse n'abategetsi, nta gutakaza amakuru y'ibanga.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, ishyirahamwe TCN Coalition ryashyizweho n'imiryango yunze ubumwe nyuma y'uko habonetse uburyo bwo kugabanya ubwandu, hagamijwe kugabanya ubwandu bw'icyorezo binyuze mu gushyiraho uburyo bwo kucyikuraho ku isi hose.
Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yashyize BlueTrace ku mugaragaro binyuze kuri porogaramu ya leta.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, abafatanyabikorwa bayo bafite porogaramu za terefone za Android na iOS, batangaje uburyo bushya bwo kugenzura amakuru, byitezwe ko bizatuma abantu barushaho gusobanukirwa, binyuze mu guhuza ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth Low Energy na message-based storage.
Nanone kandi, batanze amabwiriza arebana n'ibyo.
Ku ruhande rwa Apple na Google, iri tegeko rizaboneka mu byiciro bitatu:
Gushyiraho ibikoresho byo gukemura ibibazo by'abategetsi byerekana uburyo bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira rya coronavirus byakozwe n'abategetsi kandi byateguwe.
Gushyiraho porogaramu ya Google na Apple kuri porogaramu ya iOS na Android kugirango ubone ibisubizo by'ibibazo by'ubudehe n'umutekano binyuze mu gutangiza uburyo bwo gusuzuma uburyo porogaramu ikoreshwa, hanyuma ukayikuramo nk'uko byahoze mbere mugihe icyorezo cyarangiye.
B'Drug testing (uzwi nka drug re-testing, re-profiling, re-tasking cyangwa modifying treatment) ni isuzuma rya mbere ry'imiti ikoreshwa mu kuvura indwara runaka cyangwa se izindi ndwara zagiye zikoreshwa mbere.
Reba ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu kiganiro kimwe cyakurikiyeho kugira ngo hatangwe umuti udakingiye kandi w'ingirakamaro wo kuvura COVID-19.
Ubundi bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 bwagaragaje ko SARS-CoV ifite poroteyine 66 zishobora guhuza umuti, buri poroteyine ikaba ifite uruhu rw'ubumwe.
Gushyiraho izi ngamba ni ngombwa mu gukora umuti wa virusi wa COVID-19.
Mu byiciro by'ibanze bya SARS-CoV-2 harimo protease isa na papain, RNA-dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein, na ADP ribophosphatase.
Hussein AA, et al. basuzumye imiti y'igerageza yakoreshejwe mu igerageza ry'ibanze ry'ubushakashatsi, bagaragaza ko hari imiti myinshi ikoreshwa mu igerageza ry'ubushakashatsi, ndetse n'indi ishobora kuba umuti ukomeye urwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'igerageza ry'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubuvuzi.
Chloroquine ni umuti w'ibimera ushobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura izindi ndwara.
Ku ya 18 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine bishobora kuba biri mu miti iri mu igeragezwa mu bitaro bya Solidarity.
Guverineri Andrew Cuomo yatangaje ko igerageza rya leta ya New York ku miti ya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine rishobora gutangira ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe.Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, FDA yahagaritse ikoreshwa rya hydroxychloroquine sulfate na chloroquine phosphate mu gihe hari icyemezo cy'ubuziranenge (EUA).
Ikigo cy'ubuziranenge mu by'ubuvuzi cya FDA cyemeje ko iyi miti ari yo yonyine ifasha mu gupima indwara, ariko cyemeje ko n'iyo umuntu yaba ari mu bitaro ariko akaba atazi kwivuza, aba agomba kwivuza.
CDC ivuga ko "gukoresha, gutanga, cyangwa gutwara hydroxychloroquine mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi cyangwa mu buryo bwo kuvura SARS-CoV-2" nta ngaruka bigira.
Abaganga bavuga ko bakoresha imiti iyo "nta yandi mahitamo" afite.
Hari ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi cyo muri Turukiya kiri i Istanbul cyasuzumye ibindi bintu birimo chloroquine na zinc, vitamine A, vitamine C na vitamine D.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'abahanga mu by'amategeko bo muri kaminuza ya Duke na Oxford.
NYU Langone Medical School irimo gukora igerageza ku burinzi n'akamaro ko gufata hydroxychloroquine nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda.
Ibizamini byakozwe mu bitaro by'Abashinwa biri i Wuhan n'i Shenzhen byavuze ko favipiravir ari "igikorwa cy'ingirakamaro".
Abarwayi 35 bo mu mujyi wa Shenzhen bagaragaye ko batanduye mu minsi 4, mu gihe abarwayi 11 muri 45 bongeye kugaruka mu minsi mike.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan ku barwayi 240 barwaye pneumonia, kimwe cya kabiri cyabo bakingiwe favipiravir ikindi cya kabiri cyabo bakingiwe umifenovir.
Ikigo cy'Ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani cyamenyesheje abaturage ko ibizamini by'ubuvuzi by'iyi miti bitaratangira.
Ku ya 2 Mata, Ubudage bwatangaje ko buzajya bwimurira iki kiyobyabwenge mu Buyapani kubera ko cyari cyamaze gushyirwa mu gisirikare, kugira ngo kijye gikwirakwizwa mu bigo by'ubuvuzi, kandi kizaboneke mu kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Mu kinyamakuru South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe yasabye leta ya Trump ko yakwifashisha imiti. Iyi miti ishobora kuba idakwiriye mu kuvura abarwayi barwaye, kandi virusi ishobora kuba yarapfuye.
Abagore batwite cyangwa abashaka kugabanya umubyibuho bashobora kubikoresha nabi.
Ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya lopinavir/ritonavir (Kaletra), ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi, bwagaragaje ko "nta ngaruka z'ingenzi zibonetse".
Iyi miti yagaragaye ko ifata virusi itera SIDA binyuze mu kwanduza umuntu ikoresheje protease.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kaminuza ya Colorado ryashakaga guhindura imiti kugira ngo ribone umuti ushobora guhuza na protease ya SARS-CoV. Hari n'abajyanama b'abashakashatsi mu rwego rwo gutunganya ibikoresho byo gupima imiti ya virusi itera SIDA.
WHO yasimbuye lopinavir/ritonavir mu igerageza ry'igihugu cy'ubumwe.
Remdesivir ikorwa na Gilead Sciences nk'umuti wa Ebola na Marburg virus. Gilead Sciences kandi yabonye ko Remdesivir ifite ubushobozi bwo kwica virusi mu buryo bwa in vitro ku mikorobe nyinshi zirimo filo-, pneumo-, paramyxo-, na coronaviruses.
Kimwe mu bintu bituma virusi idahita ikwirakwira ni uko ihita ihinduka, ibyo bikaba byatuma ikwirakwira cyane.
Hari n'ubundi bushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere y'uko ikoreshwa ry'iyi miti buvuga ko ishobora gutuma umuntu agira uburwayi bw'ikirere igihe kirekire.Hari ibizamini bibiri by'ubuvuzi birimo gukorwa, kimwe cyakozwe n'ibitaro bya Cleveland University; kimwe cyakozwe ku bantu bafite uburwayi bw'ikirere, ikindi cyakozwe ku bantu bafite uburwayi bw'ikirere.
Hari ibizamini bitatu byo mu bitaro by'uburyo vitamine C isohoka mu maraso y'abantu bari mu bitaro bafite COVID-19 idakira; bibiri by'abarwayi ba placebo (Ubushinwa, Kanada) n'imwe itarimo abarwayi (Ubutaliyani).
Leta ya New York yatangiye igerageza ku cyorezo cya azithromycin ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe 2020.
Ikigo cy'igihugu cy'Ubuyapani gishinzwe ubuzima ku isi n'ubuvuzi (NCGM) kirimo gutegura ibizamini by'ubuvuzi bya Teijin's Alvesco (ciclesonide), umuti wa korticosteroid urwanya indwara z'ibicurane, mu kuvura abarwayi badafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwa coronavirus nshya.
Ubwoko bwa 2 bwa angiotensin-converting enzyme, icyiciro cya II cy'igeragezwa ry'ubwandu n'abarwayi 200 batoranyijwe mu barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye, kiri mu bitaro muri Danimarike, Ubudage, na Otirishiya mu rwego rwo kumenya ingaruka zo kuvura.
Abashakashatsi bo mu kigo cy'umutima cya Montreal muri Canada barimo kwiga ku ngaruka colchicine igira ku kugabanya ubukana bw'indwara z'ubuhumekero mu barwayi bafite ibimenyetso bya COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi, bwitwa COLCORONA, bwakoze ku bantu 6000 bafite imyaka cyangwa irenga basanganywe ubwandu bwa COVID-19 kandi bafite ibimenyetso bidasaba kujya kwa muganga.
Abagore batwite cyangwa abatakiriho cyangwa abatakiriho ntibazabyemere.
