Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 300 bugamije gusuzuma ingaruka za enoxaparin sodium mu kwivuza no mu kuvura, bwashyizwe ahagaragara mu Butaliyani ku itariki ya 14 Mata.
Kubera ko SARS-CoV-2 ari virusi, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko hari imiti ishobora kwica virusi z'ubwandu bwa mbere, urugero nka MERS, SARS na virus ya West Nile.
