Bimwe mu bisubizo by'imiti ya COVID-19 bishobora gukoreshwa:
Tocilizumab (Anti-IL-6 receptor): Ubushinwa bwemeye ko ikoreshwa.
Nanone kandi, mu Butaliyani no mu Bushinwa, hakorewe igerageza ku cyorezo cya Tocilizumab#COVID-19.
Icyiciro cya B-A COVID-19 ni cyo cyiciro cy'urukingo rwemewe ku cyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Nubwo nta rukingo rwarangije kugeragezwa mu bitaro, hari gahunda zitandukanye ziri gukorwa zo gukora urukingo nk'urwo.
Muri Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko ritekereza ko urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2, virusi itera iyo ndwara, ruzabaho mbere y'uko abantu 18 bavuka.
Ibipimo bitandatu by'ibanze byashingiye ku myitozo y'amahoro yo mu Ntambara ya Mbere y'Isi yose yabaye muri Mata.
COVID-19 yagaragaye mu Ukuboza 2020.
Icyorezo cyibasiye isi cyabaye mu 2020, bituma amafaranga menshi atangira gukoreshwa ndetse n'abahanga mu bushakashatsi bakora bagashakisha urukingo.
Amashyirahamwe menshi arimo akora ubushakashatsi ku binyabuzima kugira ngo ashobore gukora urukingo rwa SARS-CoV-2.
Mu kwezi kwa kane, uburyo CEPI yakoresheje mu gutangiza urukingo bwagaragaje ko ari uguhutaza, ubwihindurize, gukorana n'abaturage benshi, no kutagira icyo umuntu atangaza.
Muri Mata, impuguke za CEPI zatangaje ko hari uburyo 10 bugiye gukorwaho ubushakashatsi ndetse no gutangira mu ntangiriro za 2020 mu rwego rwo gukora urukingo rukora neza rwa COVID-19.
Urutonde rw'ingenzi rw'inyigisho z'amahoro z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye I, zirimo:
nucleic acid (DNA na RNA) (Umushinga w'icyiciro cya mbere n'icyiciro cya mbere cy'urukingo: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
virusi y'icyorezo (umushinga wa mbere w'inkingo z'igerageza: CanSino Biologics, adenovirus type 5 vector)
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'abayobozi ba CEPI muri Mata, inkingo 115 z'igerageza zirimo gutegurwa, 78 ni zo zikiri mu bikorwa (79, nk'uko byagaragajwe n'ikigo cya Milken), naho 37 ni zo zimaze gutangwa, ariko amakuru ya rubanda arahari (azashyirwa kuri gahunda cyangwa ahitirwemo).
Ibipimo bya virusi I-II byasuzuguye ibipimo by'ubuziranenge n'imiti, byitwa ko ari ibipimo by'ubwandu, byafashwe na placebo, kandi mu bice byinshi, byashoboraga kugaragaza ko hari umuti uhagije.
