Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangije "SOLIDARITY Trial" igamije gusuzuma ibyago byo kuvura imiti ine y'ubwoko butandukanye.
Nta rukingo rubaho, ariko hari amatsinda menshi akora ku rukingo rw'igerageza.
Imikorere y'ubwandu bushingiye kuri SARS-CoV ni ingirakamaro kuri SARS-CoV BE kuko cOv-2 zombi zikora ku buryo bwa ACE2 mu gihe zigiye mu mubiri w'umuntu.
Hari uburyo bwo gukingira ubu bushakishwa.
Mbere na mbere, abashakashatsi bashakaga kwerekana urukingo rwa virusi.
Gukora kuri virusi, yaba ikora cyangwa itarapfa, bisaba ko umubiri w'umuntu ugira ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'ubundi bwoko bushya bwa COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, ari bwo gukingira ubwoko bw'imiti, bugamije gukora urukingo rwica ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku bwoko runaka bwa virusi.
Mu bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubushakashatsi nk'ubu bwerekeranye na poroteyine ya S-spike ituma virusi ikora mu cyuma gikora ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni ubwo gukoresha intanga za nucleic acid (DNA cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo kuvumbura urukingo).
Ibipimo by'urukingo ku buryo bumwe bigomba gusuzumwa ku bijyanye n'umutekano n'ibikoresho.Ku wa 16 Werurwe 2020, urukingo rwa mbere rwatangiye kugeragezwa ku bantu bane.
Baital afite uruhu rw'umuntu udafite ubukana rwifashishije virusi.Umushinga w'imiti washyizeho umuti ushobora kuvura SARS-CoV-2, ariko abandi bashakashatsi barawushyigikiye.
Hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 byakozwe kuva muri Mata 2020.
Ibipimo 62 by'imiti byasuzumwe mu buvuzi bw'ibimera, hamwe n'ubushakashatsi bune bwa hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Imiti ya virusi itera SIDA ni yo ikomeje gukorwaho ubushakashatsi mu Bushinwa, kandi mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Mata, ibipimo bya Remdesivir byo mu cyiciro cya III byatangiye kugeragezwa mu bihugu byinshi.
Amasezerano y'imikoreshereze y'inkingo za COVID-19 z'ubu zitangiye kugaragara mu kwezi kwa Mata 2020.
Hari icyizere cy'uko umuti wa remdesivir uzatangira gukoreshwa muri Werurwe 2020.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, habonetse umusaruro mwiza mu barwayi bafatiraga umuti wa remdesivir mu buryo bwitondewe.
Ibizamini bya Covid III byakozwe muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani.Chloroquine, mu ntangiriro yagaragaye ko ifite akamaro mu kuvura malaria, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020, igaragaza ibisubizo bya mbere.
Icyakora, hari ibyo abantu bashidikanyaho.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Koreya n'iya Ubushinwa byasabye ko abantu bakoresha chlorokine.
Ariko kandi, Ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe Virology, kivuga ko gufata ingano imwe ya virusi buri munsi, ari ingenzi cyane ku buryo bishobora no kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yatanze itegeko ry'ubutabazi ku bijyanye no gukoresha hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu kuvura abantu banduye COVID-19.
Raporo za mbere zagaragaje ko ingano ya ribavirin ifite ingaruka ku kurwara SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bwa in vitro.
Nitazoxanide irasabwa mu byigwa muri in vivo nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi buke bwo kuvura.
Ubushakashatsi ku chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine hamwe cyangwa nta azithromycin bufite ibibazo bibuza umuryango wacu w'imiti kubakira nta bundi bushakashatsi. Oseltamivir igaragaza SARS-CoV-2 in vitro kandi ifite uruhare mu kuvura COVID-19.
Gucika kwa cytokine bishobora kuba byarabaye intandaro yo kwandura COVID-19 mu buryo butunguranye.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira uruhare mu guhangana n'ikibazo cyo kubura kwa cytokine. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'ubuvuzi n'ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ubuzima mu Bushinwa nyuma yo gusoza ubushakashatsi buto.
Hateganyijwe icyiciro cya 2 cy'ubushakashatsi mu Butaliyani ku bijyanye no kumenya niba umuntu afite ubwandu bwanduye.
Hamwe n'ibipimo by'amaraso by'ibanze by'amaraso kugira ngo hamenyekane urugero rw'iyo cytokine, bigira uruhare mu gukumira iyo ndwara, ishobora no kuba ari yo ihitana abantu bamwe na bamwe bayirwaye.
Interleukin-6 antagonist ni umuti wemejwe na FDA ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku miti ya sitokine ya steroid refractory yavuye mu buvuzi bwa CAR T cells, mu 2017.
Ibi ni byo byemeza ko tocilizumab ari ingenzi mu kuvura CRS.
Kwimurira abantu bakenera imiti ya COVID-19 udukoko tugize umubiri n'umubiri by'umubiri, byashyizwe mu bushakashatsi nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda indwara.
Iyi miti yagenewe SARS ariko ntiyavuyemo ingaruka.
Kwica virusi ni uburyo bwo gukora, aho gukoresha uburyo bw'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri bushobora gutuma umuntu atagira ubwirinzi bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ibindi bintu, urugero nk'imiti cyangwa imikorere y'umubiri, bishobora kugira ingaruka.
Uburyo bwo kuvura indwara ziterwa n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, urugero nk'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ufite uruti rw'umugongo umwe, burimo kugenda buzamuka.
Gutanga amaraso ya plasma ku muntu urimo kuvura, ni ukuvuga amaraso yavuye ku barwayi banduye kandi bafite ubwirinzi bwa virusi, bishobora kongera ubukana bw'igisubizo cy'ubwirinzi.
